title.rendered: BOSS AIR AIRMAX FBSS AIR MANAGEMENT KIT

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR AIRMAX FBSS AIR MANAGEMENT KIT

Boss Air Airmax FBSS Air Management Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744!

The BOSS Airmax Air Management System setup is designed to work with and support Air Ride Suspension setups for your vehicle using your own brackets, links and air bags, or using one of our air suspension systems like the 58-64 Impala FBSS kit

Using Boss Air’s 8 valve block along with 2 of the 1.8cfm PX06 12 volt compressor and 5 Gallon 16 litre 5 port light weight aluminium Air Tank

Available in 1/4″ or 3/8″ line

Everything included for an easy to setup complete air management kit.

Please not that this kit does not include Bags, Metal Brackets or links etc.

Boss Air Airmax Air Management kit includes the following

  • 2 x Boss Air Compressor PX06
  • 1 x 3/8″ Check valve
  • 1 x Teflon braided heat resistant hose 1/2FM Flare X 5/8 MALE
  • 1 x 100% Duty relay/solenoid
  • 1 x 110-150PSI Pressure switch
  • 1 x 5 GAL 15LTR 5 Port alloy tank
  • 1 x 1/4″ Drain cock for air tank
  • 1 x 8 Valve manifold block
  • 1 x Water trap & bracket
  • 1 x Cone silencer 3/8″
  • 1 x Twin gauge panel
  • 4 x Momentary 12V switch
  • 2 x 200PSI Boss gauge dual needle
  • 10MTRS 4MM Twin airline
  • 4 x 1/4 Tube X 1/4NPT Push connect fittings
  • 4 x 3/8 x 1/4 Reducing bush
  • Instructions

1/4″ Kit

  • 1 x 1/4″ Tube 1/4NPT Elbow
  • 7 x 1/4 Tube X 1/4NPT Push connect fittings
  • 16MTRS 1/4 X 170 J844 Braid BLK air line

3/8″ Kit

  • 1 x 3/8″ Tube 1/4NPT Elbow
  • 8 x 3/8 Tube X 1/4NPT Push connect fittings
  • 16MTRS 3/8 X 170 J844 Braid BLK air line

Extra option available:

  • Remote Nitto Add-on – Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools

To view the full range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

For more 4×4 inspiration follow us on Instagram and Facebook
